<P>AN
ACCOUNT
OF A
VOYAGE
UP THE
River <HI>de la Plata,</HI>
And thence over Land to
PERU.
With Ob&s;ervations on the Inhabi|tants,
as well <HI>Indians</HI> and <HI>Spaniards;</HI>
the Cities, Commerce, Fertility, and
Riches of that Part of <HI>America.</HI></P>
<P><HI>By Mon&s;.</HI> Acarete du Bi&s;cay.</P>
<P><HI>LONDON:</HI>
Printed for <HI>Samuel Buckley,</HI> at the <HI>Dolphin</HI>
over again&s;t St. <HI>Dun&s;tans</HI> Church in
<HI>Fleet&s;treet.</HI> 1698.</P>
</DIV1>
<DIV1 TYPE="map">
<PB REF="108">
<P><FIGURE>
<HEAD>A MAP
of the Provinces
PARAGUAY
<HI>and</HI>
TUCUMAN
<HI>with</HI>
the River Plate&punc;
<HI>London Printed for S: Buckley&punc;</HI></HEAD>
