<P>A
JOURNAL
OF THE
TRAVELS
OF
JOHN GRILLET,
AND
FRANCIS BECHAMEL
INTO
<HI>G&V;IANA,</HI>
In the Year, 1674.</P>
<P>IN
Order to Di&s;cover the Great <HI>Lake</HI>
of <HI>PARIMA,</HI> and the many Cities
&s;aid to be &s;ituated on its Banks, and
reputed the Riche&s;t in the WORLD.</P>
<P>LONDON:
<HI>Printed for</HI> Samuel Buckley. 1698.</P>
